Gordhan Says Sacrifices Needed to Achieve `Balanced' South African Growth

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-02-25T06:26:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/gordhan-says-sacrifices-needed-to-achieve-balanced-south-african-growth.html
South African Finance Minister  Pravin Gordhan  said sacrifices are needed to achieve balanced
growth because ordinary actions “won’t get us anywhere,” in a
speech to business leaders in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
